article_title: Insurers May Leave Obamacare Markets, But Don't Expect A Mass Exodus

article_metadata.description: Even if UnitedHealth Group and Humana leave public exchanges under the Affordable Care Act in 2017, there's more than enough choices for Obamacare customers that should remain.
article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen
